&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of industry experience in motion design, creative design, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong portfolio demonstrating high-quality motion and visual work, ideally for digital or social platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong command of Adobe Creative Suite, especially After Effects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Figma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and take full ownership of a project from concept to delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to communicate ideas and stories visually&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in performance marketing or creating assets optimized for paid social is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Webflow is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Formal training in visual communication, graphic design, or a related discipline is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
